{"tid":1623100,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"與其聽陳雲講，不如聽哩位學者講：香港下一步［成立非常議會］","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T01:37:34.000Z","uid":216800,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0a30504f8f46e482df064041fa245d46fe016407","tid":1623100,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:21:36.000Z","msg":"首先睇咗條片先：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kjPzht_pgCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkjPzht_pgCQ&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=2db90036\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kjPzht_pgCQ</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單D黎講就係18區選出各區代表<br />\n然後組成臨時會議<br />\n作為真正<span style=\"color: red;\">民意代表人</span>同政府傾<br />\n佢無得唔同我地傾<br />\n唔傾-&gt; 抗爭繼續落去<br />\n接下來好多野條片講晒　咁我唔再重覆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">哩條路係目前最清晰既方向同目標</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔識政治<br />\n但係好認同佢講嘅野 :<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理的 建立人民議會<br />\n勇武的 保護人民議會<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"91589d6d5d85beb7dc8537e8eaefebb2bf747438","tid":1623100,"uid":70973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:24:29.000Z","msg":"同政府傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話同人民傾點組臨時政府下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395ab7accc67db82ddaba26f6723ae729daba0a9","tid":1623100,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:25:42.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"552a3a0d9402d32c9c60298b66ee50162aba4188","tid":1623100,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91589d6d5d85beb7dc8537e8eaefebb2bf747438","tid":1623100,"uid":70973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco